<li>\r\n				Increase level of customer needs first</li>\r\n			<li>\r\n				Concession strategies</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Common negotiation tactics\r\n		<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\r\n			<li>\r\n				Bogey</li>\r\n			<li>\r\n				Good guy, Bad guy</li>\r\n			<li>\r\n				Nibbling</li>\r\n			<li>\r\n				Crunch</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<u>DAY FOUR</u></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Merchandising</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Checking the store rooms for stocks.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Maximizing on-shelf availability and product visibility.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Effective product placement.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>&ldquo;Brain Sell&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		How the salespersons&rsquo; mental agility can increase so as to perform at the very best.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		How to bring high energy to bear for top performance.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		How the salespersons can identify their individual personal strengths and weaknesses and plan for self-development.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		How to analyse the motivations and priorities of key buying influences.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'August 13, 2013', 'August 16, 2013', '', 'NGN120,000.00 Vat Inclusive', '2013-08-13', 572, '6', '', 1, 0, '', ''),
