(168, 'CUSTOMER CARE ESSENTIALS', '<div>\r\n	Programme Description</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The programme focuses on the organisation&rsquo;s employees attaining:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>excellent responsiveness in serving customers</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>good service ethics</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>creativity that can lead to new service advancements</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>effective management of tough customers</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>strong branding for the company.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Broad Competencies Addressed</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to focus on service standards and improving on them.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to identify non-existing but desired standards in order to improve service processes.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to proactively manage customer complaints.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to solve problems.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to focus on specific service standards and improve on those standards.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to identify creative service approaches that customers may desire. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to proactively manage customer complaints or problems that may arise.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style=