(172, 'MANAGING THE SALES TEAM FOR RESULT ', '<div>\r\n	Programme Description</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This is a programme for managers who are advancing beyond selling to managing sales. It is to raise the proficiency levels of managers who supervise your sales people. It treats the important topics of business skills and management as desirable for profitable sales in a manager&rsquo;s respective territories:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Creating More Customers</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Performing for Profit</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Broad Competencies Addressed</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to agree meaningful standards of performance with the salespeople</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to formulate a control system to measure the standards</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to forecast sales</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to influence profit</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to motivate the salespeople to keep to sales budget</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to improve salespeople&#39;s use of time they allocate to key areas of their territories and customers</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to delegate effectively.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Contents</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY ONE</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The Job of a Sales Team Lead</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Transition into managerial role</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<spa