(174, 'ADVANCED OFFICE MANAGEMENT & ADMINISTRATIVE SKILLS', '<div>\r\n	Programme Description</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	To excel as an Office Manager, Administrator or Secretary you need to perfect your interpersonal and behavioural skills, to ensure you stay in control and on top of every one of your responsibilities.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Broad Competencies Addressed:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to prioritise and cope with multiple tasks</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to think as a manager &ndash; planning, making decisions and solving problems</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to improve communication skills to enhance relationships</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to manage your thoughts and Fee:lings and improve self-confidence</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to be assertive and therefore more effective in the workplace</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Ability to understand and develop intrapersonal and interpersonal skills</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Contents</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY ONE</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Taking Control of Your Work Life</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Understanding and clarifying purpose, vision and mission</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;External and internal customer service</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Controlling, prioritising and organising your work</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Making a long term plan to create the best office in the company!</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Streamlining your office systems</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Getting you