;sales target for the period</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;merchandising</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;other objectives for the period</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;adding new prospects and deleting &ldquo;dogs&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Relationship Management Competencies</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Offer Analysis:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Customer benefits</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;What&rsquo;s special about you &ndash; the Appeal</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY THREE</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Profitable Negotiation</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Rules of Commercial Negotiation:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;No negotiation when selling is unsure</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Increase level of customer needs first</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Concession strategies</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Common Negotiation Tactics:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Bogey</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Good guy, Bad guy</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Nibbling</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Crunch</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY FOUR</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Merchandising</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Checking the store rooms for stocks</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Maximising on-shelf availability and product visibility</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Effective product placement.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&ldquo;Brain Sell&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>How the salespersons&rsquo; mental agility can increase so as 