(184, 'STRATEGIC PROCUREMENT MANAGEMENT COURSE', '<div>\r\n	<strong>Programme Description</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This course provides participants with the necessary knowledge and skills to effectively and efficiently manage company and project procurement functions.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The topics covered will include:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>The concept of strategic and operational procurement management&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>How to craft procurement strategies, plans and programmes&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>How to develop the proper procurement organisation, policies, systems and procedures&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>How to determine the required procurement manpower requirement - composition, competency &amp; quantity&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Managing purchasing operations&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Managing project procurement&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Managing vendor relations</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Tender management&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Contract management&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Warehouse management&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Delivery / distribution / logistic management&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Managing procurement information management system.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbs