&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Working with the 3A =3P Model</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Salesperson&rsquo;s availability &ndash; Market presence/pervasiveness</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Product acceptability<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span> &nbsp; &nbsp; - Customer/Prospect&rsquo;s preference</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Price affordability<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span> &nbsp; &nbsp; - Customer/Prospects value</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	perception</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Salespersons Competence</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Self motivation</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Networking competence</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Product knowledge</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Market knowledge</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Industry/Competitor knowledge</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Presentation skills</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Negotiation skills</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Objections handling skills</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Closing skills</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Mastering time</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Managing relationships.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY THREE</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Sales Planning</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Deciding objectives</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Setting targets and milestones</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Critical results areas</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Managing dependencies.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Mastering Time</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Territory planning&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;Travels mana