(254, 'A MANAGERS PERSONAL EFFECTIVENESS', '<div>\r\n	<strong>Programme Description</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	This course is about what managers can do specifically to improve their individual effectiveness and enhance productivity for the organisation. The programme contents have been developed around seven &ldquo;Key Questions&rdquo; which managers must continually answer for themselves. The questions are:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What have I been hired to do?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What results are expected of me?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What can I do to make a real difference in the organisation&rsquo;s fortunes?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What are my bosses&rsquo; Critical Result Areas?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What Critical Result Areas should be for my sub-ordinates?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What do I value most in my life?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>What do I want to achieve - my goals: Long term? Short-term? Professionally? Socially?</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Contents</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY ONE</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Planning Orientation</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>The discipline of planning and preparation to avoid unplanned catastrophes:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;short term planning: daily/weekly/monthly</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; o &nbsp;long term planning: self development outlook.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Recognise and take full advantage of limited resources.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Focus awareness on company procedures.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Time discipline.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Business Knowledge</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Strong knowledge of the organisation&rsquo;s business.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Appreciation of their decisions and actions which touch the business&rsquo; bottom line.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Application of competence to see jobs delivered cost effectively.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Performance Orientation</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Focus on delivering results - work efficiently and creatively to meet agreed goals and objectives.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Define personal responsibilities.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Be clear about standards.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Review self performance against set goals.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Opportunities Focused</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Understand what opportunities exist or can be created, and convert them into results.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Take advantage of opportunities for success in the present or future.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Create new ways of doing things that are beneficial, advantageous or profitable.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Problem Solving</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Identify forms of waste to reduce losses.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Make adjustments to accommodate changing situations.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Respond resourcefully to new demands or circumstances.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY TWO</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Innovativeness</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Experiment and be adventurous.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Develop new thinking and skills and challenge yourself.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Initiative</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Anticipate business needs to proactively create solutions.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Take on difficult tasks in order to achieve business results.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Delegation and Empowerment</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Willingly delegate.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Provide subordinates with opportunities to prove their capabilities.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Assign the appropriate degree of authority.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Provide assistance and support.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Champion Relevant Changes</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Strive for learning and growth.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Structure process for quality and efficiency.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Developing Self</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Strive for learning and growth both professionally and personally.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 'April 24, 2014', 'April 25, 2014', '', 'NGN80,000 VAT INCLUSIVE', '2014-04-24', 282, '9', 'December 10, 2013', 1, 0, '', ''),
