(283, 'EXCELLENT REPORT AND PROPOSAL WRITING SKILLS', '<div>\r\n	<strong>Programme Description</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	For effectiveness in business communications, this course focuses on making managers to:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Become highly skilled in the use of English Language</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Write memos, letters, reports, proposals excellently by presenting their contents with mechanical precision</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Organise their thoughts clearly before writing</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Know the techniques of outlining, drafting and revising their written messages</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Practice writing styles that are clear, concrete and courteous</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Pay attention to their spellings and punctuations</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Know the rules that guide the use of numerals in their written messages.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Contents</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	DAY ONE</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The Challenge of Communicating Effectively</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>The business case</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Communication and culture.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Writing Guidelines</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Essence of effective business writing</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"> </span>Planning the writing</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&bull;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-